n>22.07.2023</span><span>0.20000000 BTC</span><span style="color:#555">5.357,38 €</span></div></div></div><div style="display:flex;gap:8px;font-size:11px;padding:3px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #eee"><span style="color:#555;flex-shrink:0">5.</span><div style="flex:1"><code style="word-break:break-all;color:#555;font-size:10px">eeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee</code><div style="display:flex;gap:16px"><span>22.07.2023</span><span>0.15000000 BTC</span><span style="color:#555">4.018,03 €</span></div></div></div></div><div style="margin-bottom:20px"><div style="font-weight:bold;border-bottom:1px solid #000;margin-bottom:8px;padding-bottom:4px">methodology</div><div style="font-size:11px;color:#333;margin-bottom:8px">The figures above were calculated as described below, with the applicable tax rule cited for each jurisdiction — for reference if a figure needs to be checked or challenged.</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:#333;line-height:1.6"><div><strong>price source:</strong> mempool.space /api/v1/historical-price (USD, daily); timestamps floored to 16:00 UTC of the price day.</div><div><strong>fx:</strong> ECB reference rate via api.frankfurter.dev (daily fixing); USD-&gt;EUR at the ECB rate of the price day; cached per day.</div><div><strong>attribution:</strong> FIFO: exchange acquisitions consumed oldest-first per exchange ledger (BMF-Schreiben v. 10.05.2022, Rz. 61), per exchange account.</div><div><strong>matching:</strong> on-chain outputs matched to ledger withdrawals by amount (three fee interpretations) within tolerance and time window; ambiguities resolved manually by the user and recorded.</div><div style="margin-top:6px"><strong>holding period (DE):</strong> §23 Abs. 1 Nr. 2 EStG: Veräußerung nach mehr als einem Jahr seit Anschaffung ist nicht steuerbar. Fristbeginn am Tag nach der Anschaffung (§187 Abs. 1 BGB analog); Fristende mit Ablauf des Tages, der dem Anschaffungstag im Folgejahr entspricht (§188 Abs. 2 BGB analog) — Anschaffung 10.05.2023 -&gt; steuerfrei ab Veräußerung am 11.05.2024.</div><div><strong>holding period (US):</strong> 26 U.S.C. §1222: held more than one year -&gt; long-term. Holding period begins the day after acquisition, so the first long-term disposal date is one year and one day after acquisition. FIFO is the IRS default basis method (Treas. Reg. §1.1012-1) absent a contemporaneous specific-identification election; basis tracked wallet-by-wallet consistent with Rev. Proc. 2024-28.</div><table style="margin-top:8px;border-collapse:collapse"><tbody><tr><td style="padding-right:8px;color:#060">✓</td><td style="padding-right:16px">price verified against user-supplied exchange records</td></tr><tr><td style="padding-right:8px;color:#b60">~</td><td style="padding-right:16px">price estimated from public daily price history</td></tr><tr><td style="padding-right:8px">mixed</td><td style="padding-right:16px">aggregate of both tiers</td></tr><tr><td style="padding-right:8px;color:#b60">!</td><td style="padding-right:16px">price manually asserted by the user (see Manual price assertions table)</td></tr></tbody></table><div style="margin-top:8px;color:#999">methodology v1 · app v1.0.0 · commit dev · generated 2024-06-15T00:00:00.000Z · disposal 01.06.2024 @ 55.000,00 €/BTC</div></div></div><div style="font-size:10px;color:#999;margin-bottom:12px">technical verification (optional): evidence bundle sha256 8a6f94a52a044d655f513b79f9759d4347c6fc777899946f56236df25e576622 · app 1.0.0 · commit dev · methodology v1</div><div style="border-top:1px solid #ccc;padding-top:12px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:20px"><div style="font-size:10px;color:#555;flex:1">technical verification (optional): lineage verified, attribution sum [1.00000000 BTC] matches disposal amount.</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:#999;flex-shrink:0">15.06.2024</div></div><div style="margin-top:12px;font-size:9px;color:#999;line-height:1.5">not financial or tax advice. this document is for informational purposes only and does not constitute financial, tax, legal, or accounting advice. price data from mempool.space and the ecb (frankfurter.dev); exchange cost basis from kraken (ledger + trades) or swan bitcoin (transfers or trades + withdrawals). accuracy not guaranteed. verify with a qualified tax professional before filing. no liability is accepted for errors, omissions, or tax outcomes arising from use of this tool.</div></div>"`;
